":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"这要怎么给你看……"},{"chara":[{"id":102300}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"为了向神滨的家伙们复仇，@一开始我就下定了决心啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"哪怕要夺走他人的性命，@你也不会犹豫吗？"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"……"},{"chara":[{"id":102300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"（我一定……要做到……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":102300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"（为了蛇之宫的伙伴们……）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"嗯……","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"呵……@看来这就是你的决心啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"树里，你怎么看？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"树里","textRight":"看她的表情，就算勉强及格吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"咦？及格？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"光","textLeft":"难道树里你们……@从一开始就打算考验青吗？！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102200}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":200,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"树里","textRight":"啊？@我才不干那种麻烦事呢。"},{"chara":[{"id":102100,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"是啊，我并没有事先跟树里说好。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"树里","textRight":"不过，@要是她今天过来还说些泄气话……"},{"chara":[{"id":102400,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"树里","textRight":"树里大人会一拳把她打飞就是了。"},{"chara":[{"id":102100,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"我预感到青和树里之间@大概会产生摩擦……"},{"chara":[{"id":102100}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"也想过最终可能会@导致你离开我们……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"如果……我就这么不回来了呢？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"就算你不认同树里大人@和姐姐的做法而离开……"},{"chara":[{"id":102400}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"你也找不到其他能向神滨那群人@复仇的办法。"},{"chara":[{"id":102400}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"根本得不到你想要的安稳生活。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"但你不是会就此满足的人。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"是啊……我一定不会放弃复仇，@以及寻求安稳生活……"},{"chara":[{"id":102100}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"所以我觉得你最后一定会@回到我们身边。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"树里大人也这么想。"},{"chara":[{"id":102400}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"至于你的决心掺不掺水，@只要带你去神滨就知道了。"},{"chara":[{"id":102300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102300,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"看来我已经被你们看穿了啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102100,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"结菜","textLeft":"呵呵，或许吧。"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102300}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"唉～"},{"chara":[{"id":102300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"青","textRight":"（真是败给她们了……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":102400,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"树里","textLeft":"你是不是在想……@真是败给我们了？","turnE